e cancer research and diagnostic workflow. The results are encouraging in\ndemonstrating the potential of machine learning methods for classification and\nencoding of pathology reports.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2019 09:11:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-19"}
